Third Department,

September, 1953.

(September 17, 1953.) In the Matter of the Application of LaVerne M. Brister, Tioga County Clerk, for an Order to Destroy Certain Court Records under Section 89 of the Judiciary Law.

Application for an order permitting the destruction of certain obsolete court records now on file in the office of the County Clerk of Tioga County granted. Present — Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon, Halpern and Imrie, JJ.
